default5. How is regularity and propriety of procurement secured and are the arrangements for detecting and addressing impropriety and fraud effective?default&#xa0;
defaultRegularity and propriety of procurement is secured in Halton as we utilise an e
default-tendering portal
default called The Chest which maintains a full audit trail of procurement activity. We have robust procurement rules and control procurement centrally to drive compliance. 
default&#xa0;
defaultOur Executive Board play a full part in procurement in terms of our rules requiring decisions to be made at Board level such as spend approval over £1M
default before commencement of procurement
default and waiver requests where our rules cannot be followed.
default&#xa0;
defaultOur Business Efficiency Board undertake a scrutiny role, they select a number of procurement exercises to ‘test’
default annually
default in order to evaluate the end to end process and to make recommendations
default to E
defaultxecutive
default Board
default in terms of the rules. 
default&#xa0;
defaultOur intern
defaultal audit team have scrutinised T
defaulthe Chest system and processes as well as select annually a number of procurement exercise
defaults
default to audit, more so
default,
default those of material value.
default The Audit Commission also reviewed our new ways of working and the use of The Chest and commended this as “Much strengthened procurement and significantly improved procurement arrangements as a key mechanism for delivering the efficiency programme across the Council” (Annual governance report 2010/11). 
default&#xa0;
defaultOur central role is guidance, support and advice as well as challenge and moderation. In Halton we do adopt a ‘team around the table’ approach in order to bring the service specialist
defaults
default together with the procurement specialists. All of our processes are standard
defaultised
default and we have fully implemented our risk based approach, standard documentation
default and a web based process which are used before we use T
defaulthe Chest to facilitate the actual procurement exercise.
